quran[20]{c,v,t}:
  17,50,"Maaku: [yo Nulaa…óo] ¬ęWonee kaa∆īe maa jam…óe¬Ľ"
  17,51,"Maa…óun tagu tawayngu no mawni ka …ďer…óe mon, aray …ďe wi'a: 'Ko hommbo ruttata men?\" Maaku: \"Ko On Tagu…óo on ka laawol aranol\". Aray …ďe dimmba ko'e ma…ď…ďe …óen faande e maa, …ďe wi'a: \"∆äun ko honnde tuma\", Maaku: 'No tijjaa nde tawata …ďadike"
  17,52,"√Ďannde O noddata on nooto…óon yetton Mo sikkon on √Īii…ďaano [ka leydi] si wanaa see…óa"
  17,53,"Maakan jeyaa…ďe an …ďen: \"Yo …ďe wowlu nden huunde …ďurnde mo∆ī∆īude, pellet, Seytaane o bonnay hakkunde ma…ď…ďe, pellet, Seytaane wonanii ne…ó…óanke ga√Īo …ďanngu…óo"
  17,54,"Joomi mon ko O Anndu…óo fii mon, si O yi…óii O hinnoo on, maa…óun si O yi…óii O lepta on. Men nulaali ma e dow ma…ď…ďe fawtii…óo"
  17,55,"Ko Joomi maa Annde fii …ďen wom…ďe ka kammuuli e ka leydi, pellet, Men …ďurnii wo…ď…ďe e Annabaa…ďe …ďen e dow wo…ď…ďe, Men Jonni Daawuuda Jabuura"
  17,56,"Maaku: \"Noddee …ďen …ďe aa∆īi…óon [ko rewetee…ďe] gaanin Makko, …ďe maraa huncugol lorra kan gaayi mo'on wonaa waylugol kadi"
  17,57,"∆Āen, …ďe …ďe woni noddude, hi…ďe …óa…ď…ďude …óoworgal faade e Joomi ma…ď…ďe, ko hommbo e ma…ď…ďe …ďuri …ďadaade, hi…ďe jortii Hinnayee Makko on hi…ďe huli lepte Makko …óen, pellet, lepte Joomi maa …óen …óe laatike ko rentaa…óe"
  17,58,"Alaa e saare si wanaa Menen ko Men halkay…ďe nde ko adii √Īalde darngal, maa ko Men leptay…ďe nde lepte sattu…óe, …óun …óon wonii ko winndaa …óun ka Deftere"
  17,59,"Ha…óaali Men nde Men nula Aayeeje …óen, si wanaa sabu fenniino …óe adii…ďe …ďen, Men okki Samuuda Naaqaawa mban yi'teemba …ďe too√Īi mba, Men nuliraali Aayeeje …óen si wonaa hul…ďinir…óe"
  17,60,"[Janto] Tuma nde Men wi'anno maa: \"Pellet, Joomi maa O hu…ďindike yim…ďe …ďen, Men wa…óiraali nden yi'annde nde Men hollumaa si wanaa fitina wonannde yim…ďe …ďen e lekki hu…óaaki ki ka Alqur'aana, Me…óen hul…ďina …ďe kono …ďeydataa …ďe si wanaa bewre mawnde"
  17,61,"Nde Men Daalannoo Malaa'ikaa…ďe …ďen sujjanee Aadama, …ďe sujji si wanaa Ibliisa o wi'i: \"Hara mi sujjanay on mo tagu∆äaa e loopal"
  17,62,"O wi'i: \"A yi'ii oo mo teddin∆äaa e dow an, pellet, si A nennanii lan haa √Īalde darngal mi bonnay …ďi…ď…ďe makko …ďen si wanaa see…óaa…ďe"
  17,63,"[Alla] Daali: \"Yahu, kala jokku…óo ma e ma…ď…ďe pellet, ko jahannama woni njoddi mon, njoddi yonoori"
  17,64,"Dillinir on mo hattana…óaa e ma…ď…ďe hito maa ngon, poo…óu e dow ma…ď…ďe pucci maa e seppoo…ďe maa, ka fidu e ma…ď…ďe ka jawle e ka …ďi…ď…ďe fodu…ďe, [kono] Seytaane fodaali …ďe si wanaa hodo"
  17,65,"Pellet, Jeyaa…ďe An …ďen a maraa doole e hoore ma…ď…ďe, Joomi maa yonii Hooloraa…óo"
  17,66,"Ko Joomi mon woni sogganay…óo on laa…óe …óen ka maayo, fii yo on …óa…ď…ďu immorde e …ďural Makko ngal, pellet, Kanko ko O Yurmetee…óo on"
  17,67,"Si lorra kan he…ďii on ka maayo, majjay …ďen …ďe noddayno …óon, si wonaa Kanko [Alla] nde O danndi on ka njorndi …óurno…óon, ne…ó…óanke on wonii te o seeraani wonde heewu…óo yeddugol"
  17,68,"Enee, on hooli O mutintaa on ka banŇče njorndi maa…óun O nula e mon damagariire [to…ďo koccu], refti hara he…ďantaake on fawtii…óo"
  17,69,"Kaa on hooli O ruttaraa on e maggo laawol goo O accita e dow mon bippooru immorde e keneeli O yoolira on sabu ko yedduno…óon kon, refti on he…ďantaake jokkitiray…óo e dow amen cukkoowo"